	if you selected an encrypted commmunication for the project&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
		&lt;em&gt;data&lt;/em&gt;: all parameters except &lt;em&gt;api_key&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;api_sig&lt;/em&gt; encrypted using the selected Rijndael cipher&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
